OL,3,CAttempted murder charge following
OL,4,CBelfast disorder
OL,6,FA 29-year-old man has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with attempted murder
OL,8,Fduring racial rioting on the streets
OL,9,Fof Belfast.
OL,11,FChristopher McLaughlin is also accused
OL,12,Fof arson attacks on a Glider bus and a
OL,13,Fhouse in the east of the city earlier
OL,14,Fthis month.
OL,16,FViolent disorder erupted on June 9 in
OL,17,Fthe aftermath of a serious knife
OL,18,Fattack allegedly carried out by a
OL,19,FSudanese asylum seeker.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
