OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782850701
OL,3,CAttempted murder charge following
OL,4,CBelfast disorder
OL,6,FMcLaughlin is further charged with the
OL,7,Fattempted murder of a man as part of
OL,8,Fthe same series of incidents.
OL,10,FAll of the alleged offences were
OL,11,Fcommitted on June 9.
OL,13,FA PSNI detective involved in the
OL,14,Finvestigation said she could connect
OL,15,Fthe accused to all four charges.
OL,17,FNo further details about the
OL,18,Fcircumstances were disclosed during
OL,19,Fthe brief hearing, and McLaughlin did
OL,20,Fnot seek bail.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
