OL,3,CAttempted murder charge following
OL,4,CBelfast disorder
OL,6,FA defence solicitor told the court he
OL,7,Fhas no suitable address at this stage.
OL,9,FMcLaughlin was remanded in custody
OL,10,Funtil next month.
